  <brief_title>Comparison of Two Different Types of &quot;Spray as You go&quot; Technique for Awake Fiberoptic Intubation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparative Clinical Trial of Conventional and Modified &quot;Spray as You go&quot; Technique With the &quot;Enk Fiberoptic Atomizer Set&quot; for Awake Fiberoptic Intubation (Atomizer Study)</official_title>
  <sponsors>
