  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether modified &quot;spray as you go&quot; technique using
      the Enk Fiberoptic Atomizer Set during awake fiberoptic intubation is more comfortable for
      the patient.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
